# Technology Stack (v0)

*   **Frontend:** [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/) 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript
*   **UI:** [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/), [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/), Lucide Icons
*   **Backend API:** Node.js / [Express.js](https://expressjs.com/) (planned for Vercel Serverless Functions)
*   **Database (Primary):** PostgreSQL (via [Supabase](https://supabase.com/))
*   **Database (Vector Embeddings):** PostgreSQL with `pgvector` extension (via [Supabase](https://supabase.com/))
*   **Authentication:** [Supabase Auth](https://supabase.com/auth)
*   **AI Model Interaction:** [Vercel AI SDK](https://sdk.vercel.ai/) (planned for embedding generation)
*   **Package Manager:** PNPM
*   **Deployment:** [Vercel](https://vercel.com/), [Supabase](https://supabase.com/)

